			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">For material inputs, refer to Hu Runqing, Diao Zhouwei, and Fu Yinyin</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">物质输入方面，参考胡润青、刁周玮和傅银银的数据</dataSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="en">None</deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromSelectionAndCombinationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples xml:lang="en">None</deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples>
			<deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples xml:lang="zh">无</deviationsFromTreatmentAndExtrapolationPrinciples>
			<referenceToDataSource type="source data set" refObjectId="43ac9052-e9ac-4b47-877f-783d34b7e56e" uri="../sources/43ac9052-e9ac-4b47-877f-783d34b7e56e.xml">
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="en">李鹞 &amp; 于随然. 中国光伏系统的生命周期评价. 环境工程 32, 119–124 (2014).  </common:shortDescription>
				<common:shortDescription xml:lang="zh">李鹞 &amp; 于随然. 中国光伏系统的生命周期评价. 环境工程 32, 119–124 (2014).  </common:shortDescription>
			</referenceToDataSource>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="en">Users of this data should ensure that they apply it specifically to the life cycle assessment (LCA) of 1 kWp monocrystalline and multicrystalline silicon PV systems produced in China. Attention should be paid to the methodological boundaries regarding disposal processes and their respective environmental impacts. When using this data, include considerations for end-of-life treatment and recycling where applicable. Any material inputs should be cross-referenced with the work of Hu Runqing, Diao Zhouwei, and Fu Yinyin for accuracy and consistency. It is recommended to be aware of the technological advancements in the PV industry that might affect the relevance of this data over time.</useAdviceForDataSet>
			<useAdviceForDataSet xml:lang="zh">使用此数据的用户应确保专门将其应用于在中国生产的1 kWp单晶硅和多晶硅光伏系统的生命周期评估（LCA）。在处理过程及其各自的环境影响的方法学界限方面应予以关注。使用这些数据时，应包括适用的废弃处理和回收利用的考量。任何材料输入都应与胡润青、刁周玮和傅银银的工作相对照，以确保准确性和一致性。建议关注可能会随时间影响此数据相关性的光伏行业技术进步。</useAdviceForDataSet>
